{"tid":293125,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國高鐵受困廈門隧道 乘客缺氧跳車","createTime":"2017-06-22T02:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T11:33:05.000Z","uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e93cdf9130ab9e7579686f6ebd87670189da495","tid":293125,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T02:02:34.000Z","msg":"陸高鐵受困廈門隧道 乘客缺氧跳車<br />\n<br />\n南方都市報報導，21日一輛從中國大陸廣東深圳開往福建福州的高鐵，在經過隧道時發生故障，在隧道內停了約2個小時，有乘客受不了高溫缺氧硬是跳下車。<br />\n<br />\n這輛高鐵21日下午1時54分由深圳開出，傍晚6時多在經過福建廈門一處隧道時發生故障，緊急停車。直到晚上9時車內的燈光和空調才又啟動。<br />\n<br />\n期間車廂內一片漆黑、高溫缺氧，溫度達攝氏35度。有些乘客受不了，不顧工作人員阻撓，堅持下車，但工作人員仍一直勸他們回到車上。<br />\n<br />\n車上乘客透過社群平台微博表示，等待維修人員修復的2個多小時內，車裡沒有空調、燈光，「一定要等批准才能開門」，感覺很絕望。<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/5641/2539171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5641%2F2539171&d=MMCia7h7ZnaEcZ%2FHRxIRezANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=14108487\" target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/5641/2539171</a>"},{"pid":"2b612d275bfe127f124343f2546ae9abf5d1f9f5","tid":293125,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T02:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbdc5048c068fa4b868e3c848e83e0f249c57112","tid":293125,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T02:04:34.000Z","msg":"幾時到地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569a42ab494b8035a04967d8cc5a1ad41d1ecf4c","tid":293125,"uid":73722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T02:06:23.000Z","msg":"居然無爆炸，負皮"},{"pid":"b3d6f562dc8d2feee220a9d084aceba9fb02a305","tid":293125,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T02:06:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾時到地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高鐵香港段就快通車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":